text:
2016 Baja 1000 motorcycle race
It was critical time wise to get the motorcycle in San Diego ready for pick up to attempt the Baja 1000
Thank you guys for doing exactly what you promised
We only had a day to get the bike to contingency having an entire crew dependent on the race machine arriving on time
